task.summary: Removed singleTask as launch mode, because I don't think it's needed.
Some Gradle-updates automatically fixed by Android Studio
Changed name of class with names of actions from Actions to ActionNames.
Changed socket connect timeout, and also the criteria for quit reading from the connected socket's input stream.
Some changes automatically made by Android Studio
Moved code for connecting to TOR and publishing hidden service to a dedicated namespace and class
Added class for keeping track of connectivity, like network type, if connected or not, IP, etc.
Added check for changed network location, file friendly location name, and different TOR-directories (and thus swapping of onion-addresses) for each location
Added singleTask again, just to make sure., due to some inconsitencies observed during debugging.
